OL,16,     GJurassic Coast and digs in the
OL,17,     Gfootsteps of renowned fossil
OL,18,     Ghunter Mary Anning before moving
OL,19,     Ginto Devon and fulfilling her
OL,20,     Gdream of driving a vintage tram.
